data.description: Welcome home to this charming rancher with a basement. This home offers 6 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. This was a custom built home in the Mont Vista Subdivision that has an upgraded floor plan with a master suite on the main level and the basement.  Grab bars, walk in showers and wider door ways were designed to accommodate multigenerational living but would also be great for any big family. This home also features big Windows that let in lots of natural light, custom trim work through out, and full wet bar in the basement family room. There is a door off the dining room that connects to the deck that overlooks the backyard. Established landscaping and over sized 2 car garage. This west end subdivision is located next to walking paths, parks, grocery store, and restaurants.
